00:53:12.273 --> 00:53:15.775
Hej, Gary. Slišal sem,
da je tvoj dolg zapadel.

00:53:18.112 --> 00:53:19.279
Ne!

00:53:22.950 --> 00:53:26.119
Sem pridi.
–Poravnaj dolgove!

00:53:26.954 --> 00:53:29.122
Umakni se!
–Živjo, Crystal.

00:53:33.460 --> 00:53:37.171
Kje je naš denar?
–Vrni nam denar. –Drekač!

00:53:37.339 --> 00:53:38.756
Prosim, ne.

00:53:44.763 --> 00:53:48.016
Sit sem te, Eddie.
–Žri! –Daj denar, Eddie!

00:53:48.183 --> 00:53:49.601
Nočeš tega, Eddie!

00:54:00.487 --> 00:54:02.822
Poberi se, Angela!
Pojdi stran!

00:54:12.166 --> 00:54:15.418
Jaz sem Mesar.
–Jaz pa Požigalka.

00:54:15.586 --> 00:54:19.088
Zakaj govorita s tako
nizkimi glasovi? –Ker sva kul.

00:54:19.256 --> 00:54:23.009
Daj še ti. –V redu.
