01:00:01.515 --> 01:00:04.850
Ja. –Res je.
–Kateri ustanovi?

01:00:05.352 --> 01:00:09.146
Obrezovanje konjev.
–Jasnovidne otroke –Za Kanado.

01:00:09.815 --> 01:00:11.023
Kje je denar?

01:00:11.191 --> 01:00:13.276
To je smešno.
