01:00:13.443 --> 01:00:16.779
Res? –Ja. –Povsod
drugje sva pogledala, zato …

01:00:16.947 --> 01:00:18.364
Chandler, preveri.

01:00:20.534 --> 01:00:23.536
Scotty, sem poglej.
–Ljubica, ne kaži s prstom.

01:00:23.704 --> 01:00:27.373
Poglej, kako živčen je bambi.
–Ta slika vaju zelo zanima.

01:00:27.541 --> 01:00:30.710
Ja. –Ne zanima naju.
–Samo mala srnica.

01:00:32.671 --> 01:00:35.381
